Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:48.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,never never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:49.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one more chance,one more chance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:51.15,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:04.45,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出会いましては簡単すぎるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:07.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初に決めた答えはひとつ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:09.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ときめきました合格しますか?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:12.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋も勝負もあわてない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:14.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,コツコツコツと徹夜に溜息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:17.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私のなかに天才dreamer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:20.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思うことみな叶えばいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:22.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人の世界はきにしない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:25.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect-area complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:27.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶対ここで待ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:34.35,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect-area　望む声が聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:35.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah! EAR EAR!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:38.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?　とまらないすれちがい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:41.55,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私が相談相手なら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:44.15,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「友達かい?」「友達です。」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:46.15,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しき0点だね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:49.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!　やりなおしかきなおし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:51.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本気で　one more chance please
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:55.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いまより素敵な未来があるのに
