Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:07.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,220)}{\fs14}忘加藏红花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:07.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(475,35)}{\fs14}火力太猛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.50,0:23:08.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,115)}{\fs14}放错了洗涤剂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.50,0:23:08.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(375,102)}{\fs14}黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.50,0:23:08.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(580,90)}{\fs14}盐放多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:10.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做失败了的西班牙大锅饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,327)}{\fs14}〈Paella〉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.65,0:23:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是为了做我喜欢吃的菜所以练习
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:25.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够努力  没资格生气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「努力只是完成结果的过程」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果以过程本身为荣的话  就本末倒置了」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个…笨蛋啊
