Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.50,0:25:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.20,0:25:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜欢姐姐
